  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a rushing current of water that flows on the ground at blistering speeds. Each creature in a 5-foot-wide, 30-foot-long line must make a Strength saving throw or take 2d12 cold damage and be knocked prone on a failed save, or half as much damage and no additional effects on a successful one.</p><p><em><strong>Saturation.</strong></em> If used near a sufficient source of water, reduce the chakra cost of this jutsu by 2 or increase the width of the line by 5 feet.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above <br />D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 1d12.</p>",
